      <Description>This data set contains Wind WAVES  Thermal Noise Receiver calibrated data. Spectra are given in µV^2 / Hz.  The spectra dynamic range is 120 dB [10^-6 , 10^+6 ] and an undefined value is represented by 10-10 µV^2 / Hz.
The AGC factors are given in dB with respect to a reference voltage V0 specified in laboratory.  These voltages are given for each frequency band as follows: 
Band : V0 (dB)
A : -40.34
B : -43.45
C : -46.60
D : -49.61
E : -51.62</Description>
